features: POWERFUL SUCTION: The TS10 handheld vacuum has a powerful motor with a rotation speed of up to 36,000PM/min and strong suction power. The portable vacuum is equipped with a highly efficient battery for smooth power supply and has an extra long-life lithium battery. The car vacuum can quickly and cleanly absorbs all dirt or debris, including pet hair, confetti, dust, ash, and more.

CORDLESS & RECHARGEABLE: With the car vacuum cordless rechargeable, you can free up to move around and offers you more convenience in your cleaning tasks. With a rechargeable battery and type-c charging port, the car vacuum cleaner charges quickly and takes only 3-4 hours to fully charge, and the continuous use time is up to 20+ minutes.

CAR CLEANER KIT: The TEMOLA hand vacuum with 2 different types of attachments for efficient suction and deep cleaning (dusting brush*1, crevice nozzle*1), dusting brush for keyboards, carpets, rugs, etc, and crevice nozzle for cleaning sofas, crevices, and corners, essential car accessories for women or men, these small tools vacuum are better suited to your cleaning needs.

MINI & PORTABLE: With its lightweight compact design of 11*4*4 inches, you can put your mini handheld vacuum anywhere in your drawer, desk, or vehicle and take it out whenever you need it. We have also included a storage bag for your car essentials, making it easy to carry around with you for home and vehicle cleaning.

WARM TIPS: Beware of water ingress, wet objects may cause damage to the hand held vacuum's motor. The HEPA filter is washable, but after washing it must be dried before putting it into the dust collection hood. Regular cleaning of the washable filter can effectively prevent loss of suction and clogging and maintain good suction power.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Compact, does the job
reviews.reviewText: This cordless vacuum is tiny and weighs nothing. Charge it via USB. I don’t have pets, so can’t comment on pet hair, but it took up small stones, dirt and pine needles from the floor mats in my car. I was able to vac the entire car with one charge…may be able to use it a second time also on that same charge. It’s not the most powerful portable car vac, but does the job. Easy to clean the filter…though note the little brush they show for cleaning is not included. I gave it 4 instead of 5 stars because it is not a really strong suction.

reviews.reviewText: 仕事でPC内部などホコリを大量に処理する事があり、以前から使っていたクリーナーでは対応出来ず購入してみました。持ち運ぶには少々かさばりますが、重過ぎるという事もなくその分ダストカップは大きめで吸引力も素晴らしいです。以前に18000paと謳う商品を使ってみましたが、それよりしっかりと吸い込んでくれました。音は流石に大きいですが、仕事の効率が上がったので良しとします。スイッチがスライド式なのでバッグ内で誤作動しにくい点も、個人的に高評価ポイントです。
Molto comodo. Potrebbe però essere più potente
